sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant BFF as BFF
    participant WO as Workflow Orchestrator
    participant PS as Prompt Service
    participant GI as Guardrails Input Check
    participant MG as Model Gateway
    participant L1 as Primary LLM
    participant L2 as Secondary LLM
    participant DF as Deterministic Fallback
    participant GO as Guardrails Output Check
    participant AP as Approval Policy / HITL
    participant AUD as Audit / Observability

    U->>BFF: Submit AI request
    BFF->>WO: Forward request
    WO->>PS: Build prompt/context
    PS-->>WO: Prompt ready
    WO->>GI: Validate input

    alt Input blocked
        GI-->>WO: Reject / sanitize required
        WO->>AUD: Log blocked input
        WO-->>BFF: Safe failure response
    else Input valid
        GI-->>WO: OK
        WO->>MG: Invoke model
        MG->>L1: Call primary LLM

        alt Primary success
            L1-->>MG: Response
        else Primary fails
            L1-->>MG: Timeout / error
            MG->>L2: Call secondary LLM

            alt Secondary success
                L2-->>MG: Response
            else Secondary fails
                L2-->>MG: Timeout / error
                MG->>DF: Build deterministic fallback
                DF-->>MG: Fallback response
            end
        end

        MG-->>WO: Model/fallback response
        WO->>GO: Validate output

        alt Output unsafe but repairable
            GO-->>WO: Repaired output
        else Output unsafe and not repairable
            GO-->>WO: Block / Manual Review
            WO->>AUD: Log output policy failure
            WO-->>BFF: Review required response
        else Output safe
            GO-->>WO: OK
            WO->>AP: Check action policy

            alt Approval required
                AP-->>WO: Create approval task / wait for HITL
            else Advisory only
                AP-->>WO: No approval needed
            end

            WO->>AUD: Log success / fallback / approval path
            WO-->>BFF: Final response
        end
    end

    BFF-->>U: Response